                "@value": "Other versions:\ncriterion for the mandate that gives power to an agent to represent a legal entity\ncriterion for power to one or several agents to represent a legal entity\nThe capacity to act on behalf.. is from here https://everis-rpam.github.io/Glossary.html#C"
            },
